Trying to stay consistent and motivated is one of the hardest thing I’ve ever had to do in my life. Show up every day with SO MANY excuses and reasons to NOT show up. Sometimes it feels like giving our best is not enough, that we have to push through and give it even more - find a new highest best I guess. Anyways, I’ll keep trying and doing whatever I can to stay on the right path towards my goals! 💪🏼 #fitnessmotivation #goals #fitnessgoals #gay #gym #workout #homeworkout #keepgoing #consistency

latestPosts.caption: I think life is just a bunch of “restarting” over and over. It’s so hard to stay focused on a goal, no matter what the goal is, if it needs, discipline, hard work, saying no, showing up every day, fighting your own thoughts and making it through life and all its “surprises” - well, good luck. Anyways. Here I am again, following a path of health and exercise AGAIN, and hoping and working to stay in it. Keep moving my friends. Life is short! #life #fitness #workout #gym #gay #actor #goals #motivation
